#overview
Some of the security products of Asiainfo and TrendMicro are similar. Trend micro's entire business in China has been acquired by Asininfo several years ago.The following security products or solutions are provided by asinfo security. The content and format of the log content of the original trendmicro security devices have also been adjusted. 

This add-on is designed for asiainfo TDA, which is an ips device. 
This add-on  provides the CIM-compatible knowledge to use with other Splunk apps, such as Splunk Enterprise Security .


#data inputs
The log data of Asiainfo TDA will be collected throught syslog or file(generated by syslog-ng) monitor.
The sourcetype should be config as "asiainfo:tda", then the add-on will run happily.